<p>Studied and implemented active contour models for parametric curve and level-set curves,
evolving the curves by minimizing the mean-curvature or the geodesic metric.
A medical image is segmented using the proposed algorithms and their performance is compared.</p>

<p>The project is based on <a href="https://www.numerical-tours.com/">Numerical Tours (G. Peyré)</a>
which explores image processing among other data science and applied mathematics topics.</p>
